 Nestora PK - eCommerce Operating System

Centralized business management system for Nestora, a Shopify home organization brand.**

🎯 Project Overview

This system automates and manages all major aspects of Nestora's eCommerce operations from a single dashboard, including:

- Shopify store management (products, inventory, orders, customers)
- Order processing & fulfillment tracking
- Customer communication via WhatsApp & email
- Meta & Google Ads performance monitoring
- AI-generated product descriptions and SEO content
- Profit analytics and inventory reporting
- COD order verification automation
- Review collection & customer retention campaigns
- ├── n8n/ # Workflow automation (self-hosted)
├── supabase/ # PostgreSQL database schemas
├── nextjs-dashboard/ # Frontend analytics dashboard
├── workflows/ # n8n workflow JSON exports
├── scripts/ # Utility scripts for sync & maintenance
└── docs/ # Documentation & setup guides
